HEADWORD: fullback
<hw>fullback</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>an offensive football player who
plays farther behind the line of scrimmage than the half-back. They are
used primarily for blocking and line plunges.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> fullback.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

