HEADWORD: fullback
<hw>fullback</hw> <pos>v.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <fld>(Football)</fld>
<def>To play the position of fullback on a football team; to be the
fullback.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Full-blooded</ent>⟦br⟧
